<hr width="50%" color="purple" />
<div class=" centerText-Max1000">
    <p>
        <b>Can I return your product if I don't like it?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />
        
        yes, you can return the product within 10 days,we will give you another product or refund you
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Where is your warehouse located?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />

        Our Warehouse is at University of Johannesburg
    </p>
    <p>

        <b>Do you have pick up points in every province in South Africa?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />

        
        Unfortunetely we only have one pick up point which is in Johannesburg however we deliver everywhere in South Africa and neighbouring countries such Botswana and Lesotho
    </p>
    <p>

