    </p>
    <p>

        <b> Is it must to tip the driver?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />
       
        No, it is your choice to tip the driver
    </p>
    <p>

        <b> Can I pay cash?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />
        
        Unfortunetely our payments are made electronically except tip for a driver
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Is it possible to be involved in the process of building the PC?</b> <hr width="10%" color="grey" />
        
        You are more than welcome to join our crew when they build your Computer
